{"tid":191301,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請你講一件令你開心的事","createTime":"2017-04-07T18:09:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-08T08:39:51.000Z","uid":56790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2ec1d08dadaf862073c4f15011db2e3fcb984b56","tid":191301,"uid":56790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T18:09:32.000Z","msg":"我講先啦<br />\n<br />\n下廚令我好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己可以整一樣人人都話好食嘅嘢 好有成就感<br />\n<br />\n不過只是以前   宜家愈黎愈覺得  身邊所有嘢<br />\n都好似無咩值得開心咁<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">可唔可以分享下你自己  做啲咩  見啲咩<br />\n會令到你覺得開心</span>"},{"pid":"84ce2e5e36af6d86d941088f62d86f2f911dc0d4","tid":191301,"uid":90123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T18:11:27.000Z","msg":"諗起男朋友陪我食好野然後望住我笑<br />\n世上最幸福一刻"},{"pid":"7fef4afafd35d15aa5d2e3967ceaec5b8417d870","tid":191301,"uid":56790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T18:13:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗起男朋友陪我食好野然後望住我笑<br />\n世上最幸福一刻</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 絲打好幸福"},{"pid":"c1eb1f8b0466a8cc3a5af1ef3539e776e5a29621","tid":191301,"uid":103212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T18:19:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"350af67cae8036c715a8dbe2475c23c4591b3ede","tid":191301,"uid":87397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T18:24:36.000Z","msg":"自己奶野時有朋友擔心<br />\n係真關心我 唔係啲酒肉fd<br />\n其實都係件幸福既事"},{"pid":"af5f655dfeb223fcfe68708e9182d1fcf63fd163","tid":191301,"uid":27662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T18:27:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽日約左朋友去食二百蚊左右既打邊爐 聽講有任食長腳蟹唔知真唔真<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n介唔介意講係邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif